name: Ecotec Engine
description: A machine designed to convert one form of energy into mechanical energy The GM Ecotec engine, also known by its codename L850, is a family of all-aluminium inline-four engines, displacing between 1.4 and 2.5 litres. While these engines were based on the GM Family II engine, the architecture was substantially re-engineered for the new Ecotec application produced since 2000.

name: AMX-56 Tank
description: The Leclerc tank is a main battle tank built by GIAT, now Nexter of France. It was named in honour of General Philippe Leclerc de Hauteclocque, who led the French element of the drive towards Paris while in command of the Free French 2nd Armoured Division in World War II.

name: Aircraft deicer truck
description: The open-basket aircraft deicer/ washer was specifically designed to provide a wide range of options to handle requirements at both small and large airports. Model: CT1800 1,200 Gallon (4550 Liter) fluid storage capacity. Tanks constructed of Stainless. SteelDeicing system: 1,000 gallon capacity. Anti-icing system: 200 gallon capacity.

name: Coffee machine RTX-3090
description: An espresso machine brews coffee by forcing pressurized water near boiling point through a puck of ground coffee and a filter in order to produce a thick, concentrated coffee called espresso.

name: DJI Mini 2 Drone
description: Small drone with an integrated camera designer for high quality professional photography it weights less than 249 g, it weighs about as much as an apple and fits in the palm of your hand.  max battery life of 31 minutes Mini 2 can resist 29-38kph winds and take off at a max altitude of 4,000 meters, so your footage is stable even when flying along a windy coastline or high above an alpine forest.

name: Fire extinguisher
description: An active fire protection device used to extinguish or control small fires, often in emergency situations. In stored pressure units, the expellant is stored in the same chamber as the firefighting agent itself. Depending on the agent used, different propellants are used.

name: Feed distributor ISRK-8
description: Feed distributor with horizontal arrangement. Feeder Master is equipped with a two-stage reducer. he two-stage gearbox allows to obtain 4 speeds of screw rotation and to select the optimal operating modes depending on the type of feeds being loaded and / or their condition (frozen, wet, long-fiber). Screw rotation speed - 15; 21; 26; 45 rpm.

name: Microscope
description: An instrument used to see objects that are too small to be seen by the naked eye. Microscopes are effectively just tubes packed with lenses, curved pieces of glass that bend (or refract) light rays passing through them.

name: Smoke detector
description: Commercial security devices issue a signal to a fire alarm control panel as part of a fire alarm system, while household smoke detectors, also known as smoke alarms, generally issue a local audible or visual alarm from the detector itself or several detectors if there are multiple smoke detectors interlinked.

name: Bork kettle - K800
description: Container for boiling water, that has a lid, handle, and spout and is made from plastic or metal. - Power: 2200-2400 W - Volume: 1,7 l - Temperature conditions: 5 - Dimensions (DhShhV): 18x23x25 cm - Weight: 1.55 kg - Length of an electric cable: 1 m - case Material: stainless steel - Guarantee period: 5 years

name: Nordic Espresso Coffee
description: Machine Model: SK22110 The Espresso Coffee Machine doesn’t just look the part, its elegant design extends to the coffee it creates whether straight up espresso or a luxurious cappuccino. High performance - 15 Bars of pressure and a self-priming system means the Swan Retro espresso maker is always ready to make delicious coffees in minutes.
